  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0db8\u0db1\u0dca \u0db6\u0dbd\u0db4\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb \u0d91\u0d9a\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1\u0d9a\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1 \u0db6\u0dc0 \u0db4\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dcf \u0db8\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0dd6 03\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "03 people were arrested for extorting money by saying that passports will be issued in one day",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A former employee of that office and two other people were caught by the young people who claimed that foreign passports will be prepared under one-day and normal service for the youths who come to the Kandy branch office of the Immigration Department to obtain foreign passports. The Kandy headquarters have been handed over to the police.",
        "The Kandy office issues a limited number of applications for the issuance of passports under the one-day service, and police investigations have revealed that some of the applications were obtained by the suspects from the office and sold for money.",
        "It has been revealed in the police investigations that the suspects have received an amount of 40,000 to 50,000 rupees for preparing a foreign travel permit under the one-day service and 6000 rupees for preparing a foreign travel permit under the normal system.",
        "Three suspects were caught by a group of youths who had come to get foreign passports while taking an advance of Rs.",
        "Police say that among the three people who were arrested, there is a person who is said to have worked at the immigration office for some time, a tricycle driver and a resident of Matale area.",
        "The money of 25,000 rupees taken from the girl who came from Dehi Attakandiya area was captured by the suspects and the youths have given it to the girl again. After that, the security officers of the place tried to free the suspects from the place without taking any kind of legal action against the suspects, and after the youths at the place protested strongly, a group of officers from the Kandy headquarters police came and arrested the suspects."
      ],
